Package: sanuwave-client
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Sanuwave <support@sanuwave.com>
Installed-Size: 457
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.34), libgcc-s1 (>= 3.0), libqt6core6 (>= 6.2.0), libqt6gui6 (>= 6.2.0), libqt6network6 (>= 6.1.2), libqt6widgets6 (>= 6.1.2), libstdc++6 (>= 5.2), libturbojpeg
Section: science
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://sanuwave.com
Description: Sanuwave Medical Imaging Client
 Qt-based client application for the Sanuwave medical imaging system.
 Provides wound measurement and analysis capabilities using multi-camera
 imaging with RGB, thermal, and sensor data fusion.
 .
 Features include:
  - Multi-camera streaming and capture
  - Thermal imaging overlay
  - 3D reconstruction via COLMAP/SfM
  - Wound measurement tools
